#

Stuffed Tomatoes with Turkey and Rice

45 min
$12.5
350 kcal
Difficulty: 25%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

Dairy

Dietary Tags:

High ProteinLow Carb

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main Course

Tags:

EasyHealthyComfort Food

Description

Juicy tomatoes filled with a savory blend of ground turkey, rice, and cheese, baked to perfection.

Ingredients

  • large tomatoes: 4
  • ground turkey: 1 pound
  • cooked rice: 1 cup
  • shredded cheese: 1 cup
  • onion, chopped: 1
  • garlic, minced: 2 cloves
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • italian seasoning: 1 teaspoon
